    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Fixing 'mkmf' load error in Ubuntu]]></title>
    <link href="http://sunu.github.com/blog/2013/02/02/fixing-mkmf-load-error-ubuntu/"/>
    <updated>2013-02-02T20:58:00+05:30</updated>
